  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 11 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 2 factors marked not-applicable with documented rationale confirming they fall outside the scope of this V&V 40 medical-device assessment context.",
